{"metadata":{"extendedModule":"OUDSThemesOrange","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","role":"symbol","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B32ThemeLinkComponentTokensProviderC19colorChevronPressed18OUDSTokensSemantic013MultipleColorL5TokenCvp","title":"colorChevronPressed","symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"colorChevronPressed"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"MultipleColorSemanticToken","preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@OUDSTokensSemantic@objc(cs)MultipleColorSemanticToken","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Has for value token colors.contentBrandPrimary (= light: “#F15E00FF” \/ dark: “#FF7900FF”)"}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider\/colorChevronPressed","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemelinkcomponenttokensprovider\/colorchevronpressed"]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@objc"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"colorChevronPressed"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@OUDSTokensSemantic@objc(cs)MultipleColorSemanticToken","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"MultipleColorSemanticToken"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]}],"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemelinkcomponenttokensprovider","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of links"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"link"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSLink"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllLinkComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"LinkComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"links"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Link"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"colors (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":") and spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"title":"OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","kind":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"kind":"symbol","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png"}],"type":"topic","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","title":"Theme Orange"},"ic_theme_orange.png":{"alt":null,"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","type":"image","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ic_theme_orange.png"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider/colorChevronPressed":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Has for value token colors.contentBrandPrimary (= light: “#F15E00FF” \/ dark: “#FF7900FF”)"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemelinkcomponenttokensprovider\/colorchevronpressed","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider\/colorChevronPressed","role":"symbol","title":"colorChevronPressed","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"colorChevronPressed"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"MultipleColorSemanticToken","preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@OUDSTokensSemantic@objc(cs)MultipleColorSemanticToken"}],"type":"topic"}}}